IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
AUTHOR .HAWIN.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 P PIC 9(5).
01 N PIC 9(3).
01 R PIC 9(3).
01 SI PIC 9(10).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY 'ENTER P'.
ACCEPT P.
DISPLAY 'ENTER N'.
ACCEPT N.
DISPLAY 'ENTER R'.
ACCEPT R.

COMPUTE SI=(P * N * R) / 100.
DISPLAY 'SIMPLE INTEREST :' SI.


STOP RUN.
